title: American Horror Story 10: Teaser [HD]
author: American Horror Story 10
comment: I can’t wait!! It’s been too long, I have started rewatching old episodes of AHS because I miss it so much!!
OMG PIRATES , THIS SEASON IS GOING TO BE SO GOOD

I LOVE the way he teases us for a couple months and shocked that nobody has EVER snuck a story out to the public  before hes ready to go public. So, as much as the teases are awesome, I HATE THEM TOO lmao. Man I LOVE this series and all the mystery surrounding each season.
